entry.title: Flood Warning issued October 11 at 7:51PM CDT until October 14 at 5:17AM CDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...The Flood Warning is extended for the following rivers in Texas... Rio Grande at Boquillas affecting Brewster County. .Heavy rainfall the past few days over the Rio Conchos and Rio Grande basins has resulted in moderate flooding on the Rio Grande at Boquillas. The river is expected to fall below flood stage over the next 24 hours, and continue falling thereafter.
